# {{lb|en|grammar}} A pronoun that introduces a [[relative clause]] and [[refer]]s to an [[antecedent]]. Some words that can be used as [[interrogative pronoun]]s can alternatively be used as relative pronouns: ''[[what]]'', ''[[which]]'', ''[[who]]'', and ''[[whom]]''. The other relative pronouns are ''[[whoever]]'', ''[[whomever]]'', ''[[whatever]]'', and ''[[that]]''.

